Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}On the next Conan: 'Heiji Hattori and the Vampire Mansion (One)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.25,0:24:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Next Conan's Hint: Coffin!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Hattori, are you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.63,0:24:21.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}I'm suckin' blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.96,0:24:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\blur1}{\a6}Ah, yeah, that's next week.
